2. GRANT OF LICENSE
────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

Subject to the terms and conditions of this License and a valid, executed
Subscription Agreement, Vendorlogic hereby grants Customer a non-exclusive,
non-transferable, non-sublicensable, limited right to:

  (a) Deploy and operate the Software within Customer's own internal
      infrastructure or approved cloud tenancy solely for Customer's internal
      governance and assurance workflows.

  (b) Add Customer Configuration to Customer's designated Customer Instance
      repository, as documented in the accompanying deployment and configuration
      guides.

  (c) Add new sector profile JSON files to contracts/business-profiles/ within
      the Customer Instance, solely for Customer's internal operational
      purposes and consistent with the profile schema specification.

  (d) Create backup copies of the Software solely for archival and
      disaster-recovery purposes.

This License applies to the specific version stated above. Rights to future
versions are governed by the Subscription Agreement and the LICENSE file
accompanying each respective release.

